{
  "video_id": "XORXvaNSC4I",
  "title": "The Correct Name of the Church",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 780.0,
      "end_time": 2270.0,
      "text": "Thank you, choir."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5220.0,
      "end_time": 9900.0,
      "text": "My beloved brothers and sisters, on this beautiful Sabbath day"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9900.0,
      "end_time": 13660.0,
      "text": "we rejoice together in our many blessings from the Lord."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13660.0,
      "end_time": 18100.0,
      "text": "We are very grateful for your testimonies of the restored"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18100.0,
      "end_time": 22500.0,
      "text": "gospel of Jesus Christ, for the sacrifices you&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22500.0,
      "end_time": 27750.0,
      "text": "made to stay on or return to His covenant path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27750.0,
      "end_time": 30860.0,
      "text": "and for your consecrated service in His Church."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34780.0,
      "end_time": 37152.0,
      "text": "Today I feel compelled to discuss with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37152.0,
      "end_time": 38360.0,
      "text": "a matter of great importance."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 43110.0,
      "text": "Some weeks ago, I released a statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43110.0,
      "end_time": 48190.0,
      "text": "regarding a course correction for the name of the Church."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48200.0,
      "end_time": 51670.0,
      "text": "I did this because the Lord impressed upon my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51670.0,
      "end_time": 56270.0,
      "text": "the importance of the name He decreed for His Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56270.0,
      "end_time": 59725.0,
      "text": "even The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62370.0,
      "end_time": 65740.0,
      "text": "As you would expect, responses to this statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65740.0,
      "end_time": 69559.0,
      "text": "and to the revised style guide have been mixed."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69560.0,
      "end_time": 72290.0,
      "text": "Many members immediately corrected"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72290.0,
      "end_time": 77660.0,
      "text": "the name of the Church on their blogs and social media pages."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77660.0,
      "end_time": 80950.0,
      "text": "Others wondered why, with all that&#39;s going on in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80950.0,
      "end_time": 83750.0,
      "text": "it was necessary to emphasize something so \"inconsequential.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87170.0,
      "end_time": 90850.0,
      "text": "And some said it couldn&#39;t be done, so why even try?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 94330.0,
      "end_time": 103330.0,
      "text": "Let me explain why we care so deeply about this issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 103330.0,
      "end_time": 109590.0,
      "text": "But first let me state what this effort is not:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 109590.0,
      "end_time": 112740.0,
      "text": "It is not a name change."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 112740.0,
      "end_time": 114205.0,
      "text": "It is not rebranding."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 116730.0,
      "end_time": 120130.0,
      "text": "It is not cosmetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 120130.0,
      "end_time": 123700.0,
      "text": "It is not a whim."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 123700.0,
      "end_time": 124910.0,
      "text": "And it is not inconsequential."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 128139.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131340.0,
      "text": "Instead, it is a correction."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 131340.0,
      "end_time": 135810.0,
      "text": "It is the command of the Lord."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 138330.0,
      "end_time": 141780.0,
      "text": "Joseph Smith did not name the Church restored through him;"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 141780.0,
      "end_time": 143500.0,
      "text": "neither did Mormon."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 143500.0,
      "end_time": 149380.0,
      "text": "It was the Savior Himself who said, \"For thus shall"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 149380.0,
      "end_time": 151620.0,
      "text": "my church be called in the last days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 151620.0,
      "end_time": 154800.0,
      "text": "even The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 159220.0,
      "end_time": 166910.0,
      "text": "Even earlier, in AD 34, our resurrected Lord"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 166910.0,
      "end_time": 169640.0,
      "text": "gave similar instruction to members of His Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 169640.0,
      "end_time": 172429.0,
      "text": "when He visited them in the Americas."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 172430.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "At that time He said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 181220.0,
      "text": "\"Ye shall call the church in my name. ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 181220.0,
      "end_time": 186550.0,
      "text": "\"And how be it my church save it be called in my name?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 186550.0,
      "end_time": 190550.0,
      "text": "For if a church be called in Moses&#39; name"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 190550.0,
      "end_time": 194110.0,
      "text": "then it be Moses&#39; church; or if it"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 194110.0,
      "end_time": 198880.0,
      "text": "be called in the name of a man then it be the church of a man;"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 198880.0,
      "end_time": 205560.0,
      "text": "but if it be called in my name then it is my church.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 205560.0,
      "end_time": 209570.0,
      "text": "Thus, the name of the Church is not negotiable."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 212650.0,
      "end_time": 215480.0,
      "text": "When the Savior clearly states what the name of His Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 215480.0,
      "end_time": 219900.0,
      "text": "should be and even precedes His declaration"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 219900.0,
      "end_time": 224150.0,
      "text": "with \"Thus shall my church be called,\" He is serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 227920.0,
      "end_time": 231700.0,
      "text": "And if we allow nicknames to be used or adopt or even"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 231700.0,
      "end_time": 236179.0,
      "text": "sponsor those nicknames ourselves, He is offended."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 239440.0,
      "end_time": 242710.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s in a name or, in this case, a nickname?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 245420.0,
      "end_time": 250589.0,
      "text": "When it comes to nicknames of the Church, such as \"LDS"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 250590.0,
      "end_time": 256740.0,
      "text": "Church,\" the \"Mormon Church,\" or the \"Church of the Latter-day"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 256740.0,
      "end_time": 260399.0,
      "text": "Saints,\" the most glaring omission"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 260399.0,
      "end_time": 263170.0,
      "text": "is the absence of the Savior&#39;s name."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 266400.0,
      "end_time": 269390.0,
      "text": "To remove the Lord&#39;s name from the Lord&#39;s Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 269390.0,
      "end_time": 272900.0,
      "text": "is a major victory for Satan."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 275100.0,
      "end_time": 277750.0,
      "text": "When we discard the Savior&#39;s name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 277750.0,
      "end_time": 281970.0,
      "text": "we are subtly disregarding all that Jesus Christ did"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 281970.0,
      "end_time": 284480.0,
      "text": "for us--even His Atonement."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 288100.0,
      "end_time": 291690.0,
      "text": "Consider this from His perspective:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 291690.0,
      "end_time": 297940.0,
      "text": "Premortally He was Jehovah, God of the Old Testament."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 297940.0,
      "end_time": 300200.0,
      "text": "Under the direction of His Father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 300200.0,
      "end_time": 303599.0,
      "text": "He was the Creator of this and other worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 303600.0,
      "end_time": 307700.0,
      "text": "He chose to submit to the will of His Father"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 307700.0,
      "end_time": 309630.0,
      "text": "and do something for all of God&#39;s children"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 309630.0,
      "end_time": 312219.0,
      "text": "that no one else could do!"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 312220.0,
      "end_time": 316140.0,
      "text": "Condescending to come to earth as the Only Begotten"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 316140.0,
      "end_time": 321190.0,
      "text": "of the Father in the flesh, He was brutally reviled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 321190.0,
      "end_time": 326100.0,
      "text": "mocked, spit upon, and scourged."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 326100.0,
      "end_time": 328970.0,
      "text": "In the Garden of Gethsemane, our Savior"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 328970.0,
      "end_time": 333220.0,
      "text": "took upon Himself every pain, every sin, and all"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 333220.0,
      "end_time": 340330.0,
      "text": "of the anguish and suffering ever experienced by you and me"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 340330.0,
      "end_time": 343590.0,
      "text": "and by everyone that has ever or will ever live."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 346510.0,
      "end_time": 349789.0,
      "text": "Under the weight of that excruciating burden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 349790.0,
      "end_time": 352770.0,
      "text": "He bled from every pore."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 352770.0,
      "end_time": 357000.0,
      "text": "All of this suffering was intensified as He was cruelly"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 357000.0,
      "end_time": 362520.0,
      "text": "crucified on Calvary&#39;s cross."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 362520.0,
      "end_time": 366109.0,
      "text": "Through these excruciating experiences and His subsequent"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 366110.0,
      "end_time": 371660.0,
      "text": "Resurrection--His infinite Atonement--He granted"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 371660.0,
      "end_time": 377420.0,
      "text": "immortality to all and ransomed each one of us from the effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 377420.0,
      "end_time": 380790.0,
      "text": "of sin, on condition of our repentance."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 383510.0,
      "end_time": 385360.0,
      "text": "Following the Savior&#39;s Resurrection"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 385360.0,
      "end_time": 387650.0,
      "text": "and the death of His Apostles, the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 387650.0,
      "end_time": 392109.0,
      "text": "plunged into centuries of darkness."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 392110.0,
      "end_time": 396170.0,
      "text": "Then in the year 1820, God the Father and His Son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 396170.0,
      "end_time": 399680.0,
      "text": "Jesus Christ, appeared to the Prophet Joseph Smith"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 399680.0,
      "end_time": 406180.0,
      "text": "to initiate the Restoration of the Lord&#39;s Church."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 406180.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "After all He had endured--and after all He had done"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 418900.0,
      "text": "for humankind--I realize with profound regret that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 418900.0,
      "end_time": 425300.0,
      "text": "unwittingly acquiesced in the Lord&#39;s restored Church being"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 425300.0,
      "end_time": 430919.0,
      "text": "called by other names, each of which expunges the sacred name"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 430920.0,
      "end_time": 431880.0,
      "text": "of Jesus Christ!"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 437110.0,
      "end_time": 440500.0,
      "text": "Every Sunday as we partake worthily of the sacrament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 440500.0,
      "end_time": 444350.0,
      "text": "we make anew our sacred promise to our Heavenly Father"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 444350.0,
      "end_time": 450190.0,
      "text": "that we are willing to take upon us the name of His Son, Jesus"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 450190.0,
      "end_time": 451520.0,
      "text": "Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 451520.0,
      "end_time": 456750.0,
      "text": "We promise to follow Him, repent, keep His commandments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 456750.0,
      "end_time": 460790.0,
      "text": "and always remember Him."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 460790.0,
      "end_time": 463740.0,
      "text": "When we omit His name from His Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 463740.0,
      "end_time": 467320.0,
      "text": "we are inadvertently removing Him"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 467320.0,
      "end_time": 469960.0,
      "text": "as the central focus of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 472530.0,
      "end_time": 475669.0,
      "text": "Taking the Savior&#39;s name upon us includes declaring"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 475670.0,
      "end_time": 478300.0,
      "text": "and witnessing to others--through our actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 478300.0,
      "end_time": 483000.0,
      "text": "and our words--that Jesus is the Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 483000.0,
      "end_time": 488780.0,
      "text": "Have we been so afraid to offend someone who called us \"Mormons\""
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 488780.0,
      "end_time": 492700.0,
      "text": "that we have failed to defend the Savior Himself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 492700.0,
      "end_time": 497550.0,
      "text": "to stand up for Him even in the name by which His Church is"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 497550.0,
      "end_time": 498500.0,
      "text": "called?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 500800.0,
      "end_time": 504220.0,
      "text": "If we as a people and as individuals are to have access"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 504220.0,
      "end_time": 508740.0,
      "text": "to the power of the Atonement of Jesus Christ--to cleanse"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 508740.0,
      "end_time": 513300.0,
      "text": "and heal us, to strengthen and magnify us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 513299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519948.99999999994,
      "text": "and ultimately to exalt us--we must clearly acknowledge Him"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 519950.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521860.00000000006,
      "text": "as the source of that power."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 524450.0,
      "end_time": 527520.0,
      "text": "We can begin by calling His Church by the name He decreed."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 530690.0,
      "end_time": 532980.0,
      "text": "For much of the world, the Lord&#39;s Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 532980.0,
      "end_time": 539930.0,
      "text": "is presently disguised as the \"Mormon Church.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 539930.0,
      "end_time": 541949.0,
      "text": "But we as members of the Lord&#39;s Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 541950.0,
      "end_time": 546245.0,
      "text": "know who stands at its head: Jesus Christ Himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 549200.0,
      "end_time": 551650.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, many who hear the term Mormon"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 551650.0,
      "end_time": 554680.0,
      "text": "think that we worship Mormon."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 554680.0,
      "end_time": 557000.0,
      "text": "Not so!"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 557000.0,
      "end_time": 562380.0,
      "text": "We honor and respect that great ancient American prophet."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 562380.0,
      "end_time": 566390.0,
      "text": "But we are not Mormon&#39;s disciples."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 566390.0,
      "end_time": 568125.0,
      "text": "We are the Lord&#39;s disciples."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 570890.0,
      "end_time": 573890.0,
      "text": "In the early days of the restored Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 573890.0,
      "end_time": 579970.0,
      "text": "terms such as Mormon Church and Mormons were often used"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 579970.0,
      "end_time": 586130.0,
      "text": "as epithets--as cruel terms, abusive terms--designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 586130.0,
      "end_time": 589870.0,
      "text": "to obliterate God&#39;s hand in restoring the Church of Jesus"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 589870.0,
      "end_time": 591370.0,
      "text": "Christ in these latter days."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 594830.0,
      "end_time": 597410.0,
      "text": "Brothers and sisters, there are many worldly arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 597410.0,
      "end_time": 600920.0,
      "text": "against restoring the correct name of the Church."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 600920.0,
      "end_time": 606790.0,
      "text": "Because of the digital world in which we live and with search"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 606790.0,
      "end_time": 610819.0,
      "text": "engine optimization that helps all of us find information we"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 610820.0,
      "end_time": 614860.0,
      "text": "need almost instantly--including information about"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 614860.0,
      "end_time": 620450.0,
      "text": "the Lord&#39;s Church--critics say that a correction at this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 620450.0,
      "end_time": 623730.0,
      "text": "is unwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 623730.0,
      "end_time": 627330.0,
      "text": "Others feel that because we are known so widely"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 627330.0,
      "end_time": 629660.0,
      "text": "as \"Mormons\" and as the \"Mormon Church,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 629660.0,
      "end_time": 631650.0,
      "text": "we should make the best of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 634290.0,
      "end_time": 636890.0,
      "text": "If this were a discussion about branding"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 636890.0,
      "end_time": 642150.0,
      "text": "a man-made organization, those arguments might prevail."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 642150.0,
      "end_time": 644189.0,
      "text": "But in this crucial matter, we look"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 644190.0,
      "end_time": 648110.0,
      "text": "to Him whose Church this is and acknowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 648110.0,
      "end_time": 653120.0,
      "text": "that the Lord&#39;s ways are not, and never will be, man&#39;s ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 653120.0,
      "end_time": 659160.0,
      "text": "If we will be patient and if we will do our part well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 659160.0,
      "end_time": 663594.0,
      "text": "the Lord will lead us through this important task."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 666260.0,
      "end_time": 668939.0,
      "text": "After all, we know that the Lord helps"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 668940.0,
      "end_time": 672120.0,
      "text": "those who seek to do His will, just"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 672120.0,
      "end_time": 675110.0,
      "text": "as He helped Nephi accomplish the task of building a ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 675110.0,
      "end_time": 675970.0,
      "text": "to cross the sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 679490.0,
      "end_time": 683400.0,
      "text": "We will want to be courteous and patient in our efforts"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 683400.0,
      "end_time": 685660.0,
      "text": "to correct these errors."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 685660.0,
      "end_time": 690250.0,
      "text": "Responsible media will be sympathetic in responding"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 690250.0,
      "end_time": 691505.0,
      "text": "to our request."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 695690.0,
      "end_time": 697890.0,
      "text": "In a previous general conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 697890.0,
      "end_time": 702460.0,
      "text": "Elder Benjamin De Hoyos spoke of such an event."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 705230.0,
      "end_time": 707530.0,
      "text": "Benjamin said:"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 707530.0,
      "end_time": 711600.0,
      "text": "\"Some years ago while serving in the office of public affairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 711600.0,
      "end_time": 715239.0,
      "text": "of the Church in Mexico, [a companion and I] were invited"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 715240.0,
      "end_time": 718470.0,
      "text": "to participate in a radio talk show. ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 718470.0,
      "end_time": 722340.0,
      "text": "[One of the program directors] asked [us],"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 722340.0,
      "end_time": 725840.0,
      "text": "&#39;Why does the Church have such a long name?&#39; ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 728830.0,
      "end_time": 733550.0,
      "text": "\"My companion and I smiled at such a magnificent question"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 733550.0,
      "end_time": 737199.0,
      "text": "and then proceeded to explain that the name of the Church"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 737200.0,
      "end_time": 739490.0,
      "text": "was not chosen by man."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 739490.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "It was given by the Savior."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 742260.0,
      "end_time": 743690.0,
      "text": "..."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 743700.0,
      "end_time": 748220.0,
      "text": "The program director immediately and respectfully responded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 748220.0,
      "end_time": 757140.0,
      "text": "&#39;We will thus repeat it with great pleasure.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 757140.0,
      "end_time": 760400.0,
      "text": "Well, that report provides a pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 760400.0,
      "end_time": 765579.0,
      "text": "One by one, our best efforts as individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 765580.0,
      "end_time": 767880.0,
      "text": "will be required to correct errors that have"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 767880.0,
      "end_time": 771210.0,
      "text": "crept in through the years."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 771210.0,
      "end_time": 773800.0,
      "text": "The rest of the world may or may not"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 773800.0,
      "end_time": 776300.0,
      "text": "follow our lead in calling us by the correct name."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 776300.0,
      "end_time": 780819.0,
      "text": "But it is disingenuous for us to be frustrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 780820.0,
      "end_time": 783300.0,
      "text": "if most of the world calls the Church and its members"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 783300.0,
      "end_time": 786760.0,
      "text": "by the wrong names if we do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 789760.0,
      "end_time": 792500.0,
      "text": "Our revised style guide is helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 792500.0,
      "end_time": 796470.0,
      "text": "It states: \"In the first reference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 796470.0,
      "end_time": 798880.0,
      "text": "the full name of the Church is preferred:"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 798880.0,
      "end_time": 802680.0,
      "text": "&#39;The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints.&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 802680.0,
      "end_time": 806430.0,
      "text": "When a shortened [second] reference is needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 806430.0,
      "end_time": 812770.0,
      "text": "the terms &#39;the Church&#39; or the &#39;Church of Jesus Christ&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 812770.0,
      "end_time": 814890.0,
      "text": "are encouraged."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 814890.0,
      "end_time": 818120.0,
      "text": "The &#39;restored Church of Jesus Christ&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 818120.0,
      "end_time": 823130.0,
      "text": "is also accurate and encouraged.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 823130.0,
      "end_time": 828100.0,
      "text": "Now, if someone should ask, \"Are you a Mormon?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 828100.0,
      "end_time": 831390.0,
      "text": "you could reply, \"If you are asking"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 831390.0,
      "end_time": 834270.0,
      "text": "if I am a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 834270.0,
      "end_time": 837410.0,
      "text": "Saints, yes, I am!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 842550.0,
      "end_time": 846569.0,
      "text": "If someone asks, \"Are you a Latter-day Saint?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 846570.0,
      "end_time": 848600.0,
      "text": "you might respond, \"Yes, I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 848600.0,
      "end_time": 851945.0,
      "text": "I believe in Jesus Christ and am a member of His restored"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 851945.0,
      "end_time": 852445.0,
      "text": "Church.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 855520.0,
      "end_time": 858000.0,
      "text": "My dear brothers and sisters, I promise"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 858000.0,
      "end_time": 860670.0,
      "text": "that if we will do our best to restore"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 860670.0,
      "end_time": 865839.0,
      "text": "the correct name of the Lord&#39;s Church, He whose Church this is"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 865840.0,
      "end_time": 869140.0,
      "text": "will pour down His power and blessings"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 869140.0,
      "end_time": 873880.0,
      "text": "upon the heads of the Latter-day Saints, the likes of which we"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 873880.0,
      "end_time": 875170.0,
      "text": "have never seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 877950.0,
      "end_time": 880200.0,
      "text": "We will have the knowledge and power of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 880200.0,
      "end_time": 883910.0,
      "text": "to help us take the blessings of the restored gospel of Jesus"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 883910.0,
      "end_time": 889860.0,
      "text": "Christ to every nation, kindred, tongue, and people"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 889860.0,
      "end_time": 895350.0,
      "text": "and to prepare the world for the Second Coming of the Lord."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 895350.0,
      "end_time": 899500.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s in a name?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 899500.0,
      "end_time": 901939.0,
      "text": "When it comes to the name of the Lord&#39;s Church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 901940.0,
      "end_time": 903756.0,
      "text": "the answer is \"Everything!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 906840.0,
      "end_time": 909970.0,
      "text": "Jesus Christ directed us to call the Church by His name"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 909970.0,
      "end_time": 913910.0,
      "text": "because it is His Church, filled with His power."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 916660.0,
      "end_time": 918600.0,
      "text": "I know that God lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 918600.0,
      "end_time": 921340.0,
      "text": "Jesus is the Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 921340.0,
      "end_time": 925420.0,
      "text": "He leads His Church today."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 925420.0,
      "end_time": 931550.0,
      "text": "I so testify in the sacred name of Jesus Christ, amen."
    }
  ]
}